Title: Added more builtin views for customer related hosts/services
Level: 1
Component: multisite
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Edition: cme
State: unknown
Version: 1.6.0p6
Date: 1571247550

The overview in the dashboard and the existing builtin view 'Customers'
did not allow to open a more detailed view for the shown statistics. With
this change, all statistics link to a more detailed builtin view.
